DESIGN INPUTS (Key Requirements)
-----------------------------------
  1. Accuracy: SpO₂ ± 2% (70-100% range), HR ± 3 bpm
  2. Connectivity: BLE 5.0, Wi-Fi 802.11ac
  3. Battery Life: ≥ 72 hours continuous monitoring
  4. Biocompatibility: ISO 10993-5, 10993-10 compliant
  5. Water Resistance: IPX7 rating
  6. Display: 1.5" OLED, daylight readable
  7. Alert Thresholds: Configurable SpO₂ and HR limits
  8. Data Storage: 7 days local, cloud sync via API
  9. Cybersecurity: NIST SP 800-171 aligned

